replace into quest_template (entry, method, zoneorsort, requiredclasses, minlevel, questlevel, questflags, title, details, objectives, requestitemstext, offerrewardtext, prevquestid, reqitemid1, reqitemcount1, rewrepfaction1, rewrepvalue1, rewxp, rewmoneymaxlevel, rewitemid1, rewitemcount1, requiredraces) values (40012, 2, 493, 1024, 60, 60, 0, 'The White Stag and the Moon', 'As a Druid of the Antler, we have dedicated our lives to Malorne, the White Stag that reached the moon.\n\nOurs is the path of love and tenacity.\n\nLong ago, when Azeroth was born and the first nightfall covered its lands, Elune shone upon the dark night\’s sky with a light so bright that it struck the White Stag\’s heart. During one of his travels in the woods Elune guided him with her light which banished the fear of the dark and brought hope into Malorne\’s soul.\n\nNight after night he chased after her light, each time growing faster and stronger until the day he truly reached the skies.\n\nImpressed by his tenacity and the love he carried for her, Elune decided to make the White Stag her consort.\n\nNot long after, out of their love, our lord Cenarius was born.\n\nThis is the story as it was told for generations, one which you must know if you desire to assume the White Stag\’s form.', 'Speak to Malanys to continue your path.', 'Are you ready to embrace the beauty of the wilds under Elune\'s guiding light just as Malorne did?', 'Now that you are aware of the history you must strengthen your heart and claim these virtues as your own.', 40010, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 51056, 1, 1101);
